um Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/02 2:15:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=379.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quad kiting from 44+</span><hr size=1> What kind of mana pool did you have for quad-kiting those rhinos? I am at 202 Int plus some mana gear at the moment.<br>
