<br>
The rhinos did not break up, but I did have to recast snare.<br>
<br>
It took all of my mana + a harvest to complete the quad for just over a half blue bubble.  I can solo two undead in the Katta cemetary for the same mana &amp; get more exp.  Sonic wolf quads in Tenebrous Mtns are also easier &amp; yield more exp at this level.<br>
<br>
